573
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,190
You can't, right?

574
00:30:46,780 --> 00:30:48,750
Don't let me down.

575
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:50,560
You should

576
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,750
think about Jiali

577
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:56,710
