00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:13,200
Are you ok?

581
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:15,590
Yes.

582
00:31:16,270 --> 00:31:17,560
What happened exactly?

583
00:31:19,230 --> 00:31:20,950
Let bygones be bygones.

584
00:31:24,470 --> 00:31:25,470
Anyway,

585
00:31:25,950 --> 00:31:27,270
