00:33:55,290 --> 00:33:56,220
That one.

626
00:33:58,970 --> 00:33:59,810
Thanks.

627
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:03,230
Come again.

628
00:34:03,230 --> 00:34:04,070
Okay.

629
00:34:08,430 --> 00:34:09,470
Comrade.

630
00:34:10,550 --> 00:34:11,390
