666
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:31,520
Yes.

667
00:35:31,990 --> 00:35:33,000
Participation is important.

668
00:35:33,170 --> 00:35:34,240
For the honor of our factory.

669
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,920
