690
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:35,600
Weimin.

691
00:36:36,060 --> 00:36:37,680
You two, give it a try.

692
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:39,520
Sing it.

693
00:36:45,470 --> 00:36:46,310
Come on, then.

694
