(Blessings)

695
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:52,910
I'm home.

696
00:36:53,990 --> 00:36:54,840
Where is the little one?

697
00:36:55,110 --> 00:36:55,950
She's asleep.

698
00:36:57,990 --> 00:36:59,590
Do you know your eldest daughter

699
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:01,880
